1. *Kamera* je korisna za snimanje lepih momenta. (The camera is useful for capturing beautiful moments.)

2. U današnje vreme, svako poseduje *kameru*. (Nowadays, everyone has a camera.)

3. *Kamera* je bila odlična za snimanje koncerta. (The camera was great for filming the concert.)

4. Moj novi telefon ima naprednu *kameru*. (My new phone has a advanced camera.)

5. U džepu sam nosio malu *kameru*. (I was carrying a small camera in my pocket.)

6. Ova *kamera* ima dobru rezoluciju. (This camera has a good resolution.)